data.description: 3 Beds, 2 Baths, Mature Trees, Quiet Street & Spacious Lot! This home was renovated recently and offers a large living room, open concept and split bedroom floorplan. New wood look tile throughout the entire home, updated paint, trim, doors & fixtures throughout. Custom oak kitchen cabinets, lazy susans, craftsman detailing on woodwork, solid surface countertops, tile backsplash, large pantry and bar seating. The laundry room has great cabinet space above the washer/dryer PLUS another storage closet. Huge backyard has a privacy fence, 10 x 15 storage shed and fantastic mature trees offer great shade. The enormous storm shelter gives much comfort during spring storm season. 2 car attached garage w/ lots of cabinets, shelving and workbench. NEW ROOF and NEW HVAC SYSTEM installed in 2021. New security lights in front and back. If you're looking for a solid home in a great location close to Sayre School, this is a must see.
